26:27.160 --> 26:29.080
The other thing I think that's neat about this

26:29.080 --> 26:31.680
is there are some EBPF fixes,

26:31.680 --> 26:34.680
in particular for that copy file range support.

26:34.680 --> 26:36.920
And that is actually pretty important

26:36.920 --> 26:38.840
