33:55.560 --> 33:56.720
so you know it's gotta be legit

33:56.720 --> 33:58.760
because they've got an open source section.

33:58.760 --> 34:02.560
And the author, Mitch Wagner, proposes

34:02.560 --> 34:05.480
that the open source revolution is over

34:07.000 --> 34:09.600
and the revolutionaries have won.

34:09.600 --> 34:12.240
